Reasoning: The paper focuses on trajectory planning for autonomous driving, which falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The use of camera images and Lidar point clouds suggests computer vision (cs.CV) as another likely sub-category. The use of a conditional imitation learning algorithm suggests machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as possible sub-categories. Finally, the focus on navigation and understanding the behavior of other road users suggests systems and control (cs.SY) as a possible sub-category.
